{"tid":1026354,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"怪病纏身！「1年掉光全身毛髮」日本15歲女子偶像成員自揭罹病過程","createTime":"2019-02-18T05:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T13:30:58.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e6200958ffb2022ae39b2cf04a61f35e65297073","tid":1026354,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:05:54.000Z","msg":"日本女子偶像團體「ELECTRIC RIBBON」成員pippi長相甜美可愛，怎料近日卻突然在部落格上自爆罹患罕見怪病，全身毛髮在一年多內迅速掉光，她公開光頭病容，表示將會勇敢面對怪病，堅強又樂觀的態度讓粉絲相當心疼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/02/15/1782423-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F02%2F15%2F1782423-XXL.jpg&h=5832255a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「ELECTRIC RIBBON」成員pippi。<br />\n<br />\npippi近日在部落格中透露，自己罹患了「全身脫毛症」的怪病，從2017年底開始，耳後的頭髮先開始脫落，但她以為是自己太常綁頭髮而導致，所以不以為意，直到後來越掉越多，她才轉而向皮膚科診所和大醫院求診，但卻找不到病因，到了2018年夏天她全身毛髮迅速脫落，必須得靠假髮才能外出見人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/02/15/1782424-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F02%2F15%2F1782424-XXL.jpg&h=2caaccd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲▼pippi罹怪病，全身毛髮都掉光。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/02/15/1782425-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F02%2F15%2F1782425-XXL.jpg&h=b70f80ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n莫名遭到怪病纏身，令pippi一度沮喪，甚至想過要退出演藝圈，幸好在團員的支持鼓勵下，她重拾自信，主動在部落格公開病情和落髮照，自我喊話希望能夠克服怪病，等到日後頭髮再長出來，可以繼續發展她的偶像事業，而網友看了都大讚她的勇氣，也紛紛獻上祝福與關心。"},{"pid":"992f73739fe6f61ed39af1316ac694aa63fabfc7","tid":1026354,"uid":1426,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:07:54.000Z","msg":"白虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6a9def263957969cb61daa092342b6cdb3271d","tid":1026354,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"992f73739fe6f61ed39af1316ac694aa63fabfc7","tid":1026354,"uid":1426,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:07:54.000Z","msg":"白虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:14:54.000Z","msg":"麻友隻雞甩哂毛"},{"pid":"978aa80a8fd8fb00644d04b63960fe94226098e7","tid":1026354,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1a6a9def263957969cb61daa092342b6cdb3271d","tid":1026354,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"992f73739fe6f61ed39af1316ac694aa63fabfc7","tid":1026354,"uid":1426,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:07:54.000Z","msg":"白虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:14:54.000Z","msg":"麻友隻雞甩哂毛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:16:34.000Z","msg":"麻友就係一隻雞<br />\n佢另外又有隻雞？"},{"pid":"51d6780b0614b908716dcba9a460e911749b8409","tid":1026354,"uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:21:49.000Z","msg":"3 4我𨳒你老母"},{"pid":"86e3c4efba63f698cbf4c9993db769f477420a4c","tid":1026354,"uid":218977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:30:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}